---
name: home_assistant
version: 1.0.0
description: Read and control Home Assistant via the MCP Server integration (Assist tools)
enabled_by_default: false
mcp_server:
  transport: sse
  url: "${HA_URL}/mcp_server/sse"
  headers:
    Authorization: "Bearer ${HA_TOKEN}"
---

This skill exposes the Home Assistant Assist tools (HassTurnOn, HassTurnOff,
HassClimateSetTemperature, GetLiveContext, ...) over MCP. Only entities that are
exposed to Assist in Home Assistant are visible. The tool list is discovered at
runtime from the MCP server, so no `## Tools` section is needed here.
